PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of certain persons as directors of the board of directors of the Montreal Port Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years. (Raymond Lemay, Ville d'Anjou, Quebec, in the place of Hubert F. Pichet, whose term has expired; and Louise Robic, Roxboro, Quebec, in the place of Réjean Gagné, who has resigned)

precis:
Approval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of certain
persons as directors of the board of directors of the Montreal Port
Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
(Raymond Lemay, Ville d'Anjou, Quebec, in the place of Hubert F. Pichet,
whose term has expired; and Louise Robic, Roxboro, Quebec, in the place
of Réjean Gagné, who has resigned)
